data.title: Win An Exclusive Pair Of Tickets To See Miranda With B105!
data.meta_description: Miranda Lambert will be at Grand Casino Hinckley on Friday, July 5th. Visit Joe Danger at Boot Barn on Sunday, June 2nd from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. to win.
data.text:
The queen of country is coming to Minnesota and we want to send you! Miranda Lambert will be at Grand Casino Hinckley on Friday, July 5th.

Win Tickets With B105!

We want to send you to this incredible show. You know when you go to a Miranda show that there will be fire and a lot of songs that will get you on your feet! That's why we love her.

This show will be no different and we want you to go and experience it all. That's why we have a chance for you to win a pair of tickets before we officially do our ticket giveaway in June!

How Can You Win?

Joe Danger will be broadcasting live from the new Boot Barn in Duluth on Sunday (June 2nd) from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. During this two-hour window, you have a chance to stop by and see him AND enter to win a pair of tickets to the show. Please note this contest is only for those that stop by the broadcast.

We have set aside this pair of tickets specifically for this special grand opening event. All you have to do is download our B105 app and visit Joe during the two-hour period he is broadcasting live on Sunday.

When you get there, you will see a special code just for those that stop by the store. Circle back to this contest page and give us some basic information to enter, along with that code. Good luck!

A winner will be announced and notified next week. Please check your email to see if you are the lucky winner!
